    "title": "日本ダービーにむけて",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "さすが『日本ダービー』！\r\nいささか空気がぴりついているねぇ。",
            "enText": "That's the \"Japan Derby\"! The atmosphere\nis a bit tight, isn't it?",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 65,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 76,
                    "pathId": -7331064144851568987
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 76,
                    "pathId": -5909023175607243407
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -9117616478347048188,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "他人事のように首をすくめる\r\nアグネスタキオン。そんな彼女に\n聞いておきたいことがあった。",
            "enText": "Agnes Tachyon shrugged her shoulders as if\nshe were someone else. There was something\nI wanted to ask her.",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 74,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 85,
                    "pathId": -7880673806142888771
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 85,
                    "pathId": 3307455442532500967
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8490330133711476741,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "マンハッタンカフェ",
            "enName": "Manhattan Cafe",
            "jpText": "……ただ、少し気になって。\r\n走り方が……普段と違う気がしたから。",
            "enText": "… Just a little curious. I felt\nlike I was running… differently\nthan I normally do.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 66,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 18,
                    "pathId": 466384591862891581
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 18,
                    "pathId": -4793491774243939762
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 97,
                    "pathId": -5679656924760022097
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 97,
                    "pathId": 8810125151292127614
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 98,
                    "pathId": 5030190487515230307
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 97,
                    "pathId": 3942771600582417212
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3539976253621321398,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "……ふぅン？",
            "enText": "… Hmmm?",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 48,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 59,
                    "pathId": -146640714020943162
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 59,
                    "pathId": -7982006941075101131
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 11,
                    "pathId": -2270670577746099709
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 59,
                    "pathId": -1045257638714107708
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3654301438042778075,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "――結局、マンハッタンカフェの漏らした\r\n『走り方』の真相について、何も\nわからないままこの日を迎えてしまったのだ。",
            "enText": "—In the end, we came to this day without\nknowing anything about the truth of\nManhattan Cafe's \"running style\".",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 82,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "君の『走り方』は、どう変わったんだ？",
                    "enText": "How has your 'running style' changed?",
                    "nextBlock": 6
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "貴方の『走り方』は、どう変わったの？",
                    "enText": "How has your \"running style\" changed?",
                    "nextBlock": 6
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 124,
                    "pathId": 2035617317165733293
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 124,
                    "pathId": 3740951580356603961
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 22,
                    "pathId": -3412738250924599148
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 22,
                    "pathId": 2349278181963091168
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 18,
                    "pathId": 2397606684944124364
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 18,
                    "pathId": -1606730778203930537
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 722504389618320193,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "おやおや！　またその話かい！\r\nカフェの勘違いだと言ったはずだけど。",
            "enText": "Well, well, well! You're talking about\nthat again! I told you it was a\nmisunderstanding about the cafe.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 67,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 32,
                    "pathId": -5537261187185082400
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": -8331856366720919249
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6563648019568824241,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "それに……もし勘違いでないとしても、\r\n私が話さないということは\nまだその時ではないということさ。",
            "enText": "And even if I'm not mistaken…,\nthe fact that I'm not talking means\nthat it's not time yet.",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 76,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 37,
                    "pathId": 5895188213904024685
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 87,
                    "pathId": -4254974472351888604
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5936235680374615152,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "君の心配すべきは、今日私がどれだけ\r\n走れるのか、その1点のみで――",
            "enText": "The only thing you need to worry about is\nhow well I can run today.",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 67,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 40,
                    "pathId": 5198374928612220652
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": -5213664072780002379
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5310750286494576951,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "それ以外のことに気を取られたとして、\r\nその行為に意義はあるのかい？",
            "enText": "If you're distracted by something else,\nwhat's the point of doing it?",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 67,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 37,
                    "pathId": 7919843175039689436
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": -6011845728260623966
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6343109507982491837,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "『ン？』と首をかしげてみせる\r\nアグネスタキオンに、言葉が詰まる。",
            "enText": "\"Hmm?\" I'm not sure what to say.",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 66,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 67,
                    "pathId": -1628531438039556822
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 77,
                    "pathId": 983892476288400115
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 77,
                    "pathId": -7297040978222978431
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6996451396891933701,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "意義がないのなら、いや、あったとしても、\r\nこの話はしばらく禁止だ。わかったね。",
            "enText": "If there's no point, or even if there is,\nthis conversation is off limits for the\ntime being. You understand.",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 7892356378107173968
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 43,
                    "pathId": -7135032274722341240
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
                    "pathId": 7103205900606223554
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2474225206141659898,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "――さぁて、そろそろ時間だ。",
            "enText": "—Now, it's time to go.",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 54,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 29,
                    "pathId": 3513724504526278579
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 65,
                    "pathId": 5435057787954933189
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6494968951016526487,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "そういって彼女は、やはり説明なく\r\n控室を後にしたのだった。",
            "enText": "Then she left the waiting room\nwithout explanation.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
